362538091,'whateva'),('town02',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362546160,'nothing in firefox'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631865,'hello?'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362631879,'hi'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631880,'Anyone there?'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631882,'hi'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631888,'sorry for the sound effect'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631892,'if you can hear it'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362631897,'i can hear it'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362631908,'its like a notification'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631913,'I put it in so i could hear people'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631916,'yeah'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362631922,'its a good idea'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631940,'Im in town04 which is where you are i think'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362631948,'yeah, i am'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362631953,'I like this game so far'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631963,'its very incomplete'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631979,'you can catch, train and evolve pokemon'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362631986,'and make a friendslist'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362631988,'Although that is true, not many games have this level of complexity to it that are online'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632034,'for example, you have great graphics going, and the option to submit your own ideas, which means that this is truly reaching out to the communtiy'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632059,'I am hoping that people will like to make their own pokemon'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632085,'the system doesnt work completely yet'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632093,'but it is progressing'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632109,'I\'ve thought about it before, I\'ve got sketches and basic ideas, but since I\'m a freshmen doing varsity track and honor courses, I don\'t have time to scan and edit'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632145,'That is good though, honor classes and such'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632187,'I will have the sketching system more complete in a few months'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632198,'for now if you have a idea you can submit it'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632210,'yeah, but it gets a bit tough sometimes, you see I\'m from the place where they developed the atomic bombs, so we\'ve got a whole ton of crazy smart people in this town, that also means that pokemon is both hated and loved here'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632288,'Also, good job, if people don\'t like it right now, or are hating, just go with it. My friends develop games, but they get hate comments all the time. They tell me they just ignore, breathe and move on'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632326,'yeah people seem to like this game when they play'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632340,'well, first off, it\'s unique'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632359,'you\'ve gone with the general pokemon feeling without too much alteration'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632376,'I have only played through gold and silver'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632379,'Also, it\'s free which means that people will likely use this a bit more'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632384,'so i am basing it off of that'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632399,'I have never actually played the real games other than on the computer'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632413,'I just use playr'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632424,'ALONE?!!!!'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632428,'yes'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632431,'just me'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632445,'i ripped the sprites tho'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632457,'wow, this is even more impressive than, and the fact that you\'ve stuck with it is great'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632466,'most people don\'t after awhile'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632469,'but the coding and mapping is me, a friend cleaned the maps up.'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632475,'yeah'),('town04',11,'Rolyataylor2',1362632480,'i have been determined'),('town04',88,'Shuang',1362632505,'that\'s good, By the way