INSERT INTO `usr_letter` VALUES (11,1355966683,2,11,'I updated the site','Wooot','Default',NULL,1,0),(14,1356813586,27,11,'here is a better way','','Default',NULL,2,0),(15,1356813724,27,11,'Sorry the website is really glitchy','I am the creator of this site. On the map there is a white text input box, if you type in there you can hit enter to send the chat','Default',NULL,0,0),(16,1356822185,26,11,'a little glitchy','Sorry','Default',NULL,2,0),(22,1357274972,12,11,'I love you','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 4th, 04:49 AM </br>Meep!','Default',NULL,2,0),(24,1357452042,26,11,'Hello :)','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 6th, 06:00 AM </br>Everything north is glitchy :( but south east everything is good. I\'m gonna warp you to the town if you go east there are trainers and grass. ','Default',NULL,0,0),(26,1357807680,35,10,'hi','Boobob on Jan 10th, 08:48 AM </br>whats up','Default',NULL,2,0),(31,1358112684,41,11,'hello','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 13th, 09:31 PM </br>I\'m the creator of the site. Feel free to make suggestions or ask a question.','Default',NULL,0,0),(32,1358131144,42,11,'Hello','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 14th, 02:39 AM </br>:) im the creator of this site how are you?','Default',NULL,0,0),(37,1358395163,45,11,'Hello','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 17th, 03:59 AM </br>you can make a smiley in the chat by typing :happy:<br />\r\nor :boo:','Default',NULL,2,0),(38,1358395295,44,11,'Hello','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 17th, 04:01 AM </br>you can make a smiley in the chat by typing :happy: or :boo:<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(40,1358535958,49,11,'darn i missed when you were on','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 18th, 07:05 PM </br>Well of you log on again. Hi. I know the maps look like crap but battles work and the MMO part works too.  Hope your on again soon. :)','Default',NULL,0,0),(43,1358633412,54,11,'I didnt catch you online!','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 19th, 10:10 PM </br>Hope you log on again. I\'ll show you around the website!','Default',NULL,0,0),(44,1358641760,52,11,'whats up?','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 20th, 12:29 AM </br>is the map working?<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,0,0),(45,1358744881,45,10,'hey','Boo_bob on Jan 21st, 05:08 AM </br>what up liking the site so far?','Default',NULL,2,0),(47,1358797656,10,11,'Map','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 21st, 07:47 PM </br>www.drawnimals.com/midi/maps.rar','Default',NULL,2,0),(48,1358836211,44,11,'watch this battle','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 22nd, 06:30 AM </br>http://www.drawnimals.com/play.php?p=battleresults&amp;id=189311312250fe2db2a7dac0.92518041','Default',NULL,2,0),(49,1358836225,10,11,'this battle','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 22nd, 06:30 AM </br>http://www.drawnimals.com/play.php?p=battleresults&amp;id=189311312250fe2db2a7dac0.92518041','Default',NULL,2,0),(51,1358892514,44,11,'If you have problem','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 22nd, 10:08 PM </br>If you are playing and have a problem. use the report button. On the bottom right of the website :D<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI will remember it better.','Default',NULL,1,0),(52,1358893368,45,11,'I gave you powerful greatballs','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 22nd, 10:22 PM </br>I will add them to your inventory<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(53,1358893904,44,11,'I am giving you powerful Greatball','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 22nd, 10:31 PM </br>It will be in your inventory. You still have to lower the enemy\'s HP. But it works better then pokeball.','Default',NULL,2,0),(54,1358898872,10,45,'hii!!!','Zyan on Jan 22nd, 11:54 PM </br>yes! I loved the site! is well on his way, sure if we persevere together will be very pro!!!!!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n(sorry for use a traslator) &gt;.&lt;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nbyeee!','Default',NULL,2,0),(55,1358904564,10,11,'I never got the maps','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 23rd, 01:29 AM </br>I never got the maps.','Default',NULL,2,0),(57,1358915458,10,57,'do you want to be freinds','Shadowriley on Jan 23rd, 04:30 AM </br>','Default',NULL,2,0),(59,1358919173,44,11,'evolving doesnt work yet','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 23rd, 05:32 AM </br>I just wanted you to know that evolving doesnt work yet. I will add it in after I get the maps uploaded.','Default',NULL,2,0),(60,1358983558,44,11,'did zyan get frozen in battle?','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 23rd, 11:25 PM </br>did zyan get frozen in battle?','Default',NULL,2,0),(61,1358985294,58,57,'hi','Shadowriley on Jan 23rd, 11:54 PM </br>','Default',NULL,0,0),(62,1358999941,44,11,'Here is world map','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 24th, 03:59 AM </br>Here is world map.<br />\r\nhttp://www.drawnimals.com/midi/map.jpg<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI accidentally send you Town01. I was supposed to send you Town04','Default',NULL,2,0),(63,1359063962,10,11,'Door trim in town 01','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 24th, 09:46 PM </br>building to the left and below the pokecenter.','Default',NULL,2,0),(64,1359065061,10,11,'Another Tile','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 24th, 10:04 PM </br>Also the building on the very bottom right of town 01','Default',NULL,2,0),(65,1359096022,10,11,'BTW','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 25th, 06:40 AM </br>town04 has exits out the left right and bottom. T shape.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI set up town04 all you need to do is upload the JSON when you are finished.','Default',NULL,2,0),(74,1359591296,56,11,'World map','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 31st, 12:14 AM </br>Here is a image of the world map.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nhttp://rolyataylor2.deviantart.com/art/Drawnimals-Region-Map-w-routes-348927832','Default',NULL,2,0),(75,1359595048,10,11,'sprites','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 31st, 01:17 AM </br>http://i35.tinypic.com/n69yj7.png','Default',NULL,2,0),(76,1359610498,10,11,'I added the evolve code to the species editor','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 31st, 05:34 AM </br>I added the evolve code to the species editor, so you copy and paste caterpies evolve code to others if you want. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf i add any evolutions I will start with pokemon that start with Z and work my way to A. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nif you do it Start with pokemon that start with A and work your way to Z. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo that way we don\'t have click each pokemon to see if the code exists already.','Default',NULL,2,0),(77,1359610679,10,11,'Heres a good chart for evolutions','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 31st, 05:37 AM </br>http://pokemondb.net/evolution/level','Default',NULL,2,0),(78,1359613304,10,11,'I got pokemon T through Z done evolutionly.','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 31st, 06:21 AM </br>Tyrogue actually evolves like he is supposed too. Attack and Defense change the evolved form.','Default',NULL,2,0),(81,1359650643,10,11,'The evolution has to be lowercase','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 31st, 04:44 PM </br>The evolution has to be lowercase so instead of \'Charmeleon\' its gotta be \'charmeleon\' and if you misspell the name, it will really mess things up.','Default',NULL,2,0),(83,1359666464,10,11,'lol','Rolyataylor2 on Jan 31st, 09:07 PM </br>http://www.drawnimals.com/play.php?p=battleresults&amp;id=1690166123510adbaf025019.14408346<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI tried using mewtwo to level up ivysaur... Didnt work','Default',NULL,2,0),(84,1361325053,56,11,'Gonna update in a week or two','Rolyataylor2 on Feb 20th, 01:50 AM </br>Made all new maps for all the routes and working on npc\'s. SO it should be a big update!','Default',NULL,2,0),(85,1361990749,11,11,'hello','Rolyataylor2 on Feb 27th, 06:45 PM </br>what up','Default',NULL,2,0),(86,1362195686,11,11,'Hello yo','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 2nd, 03:41 AM </br>SEEE SHHDHDF','Default',NULL,2,0),(87,1362198668,11,11,'test','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 2nd, 04:31 AM </br>ing','Default',NULL,2,0),(88,1362199197,11,11,'send','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 2nd, 04:39 AM </br>this','Default',NULL,2,0),(89,1362889308,93,11,'I gave you 5000 coins!','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 10th, 04:21 AM </br>To buy stuff :D','Default',NULL,2,0),(90,1362973989,92,11,'I fixed your battle!','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 11th, 03:53 AM </br>Sorry it took so long! I have been at work all day!','Default',NULL,2,0),(91,1362980730,11,56,'The afforementioned creatures','LuckyNana on Mar 11th, 05:45 AM </br>http://img839.imageshack.us/img839/857/001sdf.png heres the creatures.','Default',NULL,2,0),(92,1363063633,88,11,'I fixed the lillipup thing','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 12th, 04:47 AM </br>I had misspelled lillipup in the area coding','Default',NULL,2,0),(93,1363134963,93,88,'Get Better!','Shuang on Mar 13th, 12:36 AM </br>Hope your arm gets better soon!:/','Default',NULL,2,0),(94,1363145078,11,56,'I tried out pmd sprites','LuckyNana on Mar 13th, 03:24 AM </br>http://img834.imageshack.us/img834/3709/volchimpstudies.png<br />\r\nUh... tell me which color you prefer , left or right.','Default',NULL,2,0),(95,1363362806,95,88,'READ','Shuang on Mar 15th, 03:53 PM </br>YOU\'RE SUPPOSED TO BE READING!','Default',NULL,2,0),(96,1363362908,88,95,' I am','Clhuang on Mar 15th, 03:55 PM </br>I read and play both','Default',NULL,2,0),(97,1363365451,11,95,'help','Clhuang on Mar 15th, 04:37 PM </br>I need some money for pokeballs because I can\'t find anybody to fight to give me money so can you give me some? Thanks!<br />\r\nClhuang','Default',NULL,2,0),(98,1363366701,95,88,'CLICK DECLINE','Shuang on Mar 15th, 04:58 PM </br>CLICK ON DECLINE<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(99,1363392390,95,11,'I gave you 5000 money','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 16th, 12:06 AM </br>','Default',NULL,2,0),(100,1363404292,11,11,'WOEOEOEO','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 16th, 03:24 AM </br>ksksks','Default',NULL,2,0),(101,1363404813,11,11,'ksdkfjaslkdfjlkas','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 16th, 03:33 AM </br>alksdjflksadjfl','Default',NULL,2,0),(102,1364172263,103,88,'A solution?','Shuang on Mar 25th, 12:44 AM </br>Max, accept the battle, and make a move... I won\'t respond to your move, so then, you just wait about half a minute, and then clikc on destroy battle, and then reload<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(103,1364172931,88,103,'','Max50max on Mar 25th, 12:55 AM </br>how do i accept le suggested battel','Default',NULL,2,0),(104,1364174123,11,88,'Error with game','Shuang on Mar 25th, 01:15 AM </br>So, I have a friend, and he want\'s to help test your game, so he\'s made an account (Max50max). the problem is that it just shows the charmander and the background. For me, I can only see his head, no body. Perhaps this is why people leave? He\'s using a mac, and he\'s gonna try and switch to a pc... so hopefully it\'ll have resolved itself, but it may still be an issue. He\'s also already submitted a ticket...','Default',NULL,2,0),(105,1364275673,11,88,'Internet','Shuang on Mar 26th, 05:27 AM </br>Basically, my Internet is getting really spotty right now cause the wire that connects to the wireless is kinda screwed up right now. I can still check email with my phone though, so send me an email at sincheng.huang@gmail.com, and I\'ll be able to send you the rough draft of the competition.','Default',NULL,2,0),(106,1364331443,11,49,'','Kyledove on Mar 26th, 08:57 PM </br>halp','Default',NULL,2,0),(107,1364762560,93,11,'sorry at workwork','Rolyataylor2 on Mar 31st, 08:42 PM </br>','Default',NULL,2,0),(108,1364936226,11,11,'Here','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 2nd, 08:57 PM </br>','Default',NULL,2,0),(109,1364936802,11,11,'jkkjkjkjkj','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 2nd, 09:06 PM </br>','Default',NULL,2,0),(110,1364939271,11,11,'kl;j;kl','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 2nd, 09:47 PM </br>','Default',NULL,2,0),(111,1364953625,114,11,'Sorry Go to the lava part Route 06','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 3rd, 01:47 AM </br>Go through route06 and at the end where there is a dead end there will be a stairway now. I have neglected to fix that for a while.','Default',NULL,2,0),(112,1365266232,11,88,'Rock Collector Ruby','Shuang on Apr 6th, 04:37 PM </br>There are two Rock Collector Ruby\'s in Lava Canyon.','Default',NULL,2,0),(113,1365266232,11,88,'Rock Collector Ruby','Shuang on Apr 6th, 04:37 PM </br>There are two Rock Collector Ruby\'s in Lava Canyon.','Default',NULL,2,0),(114,1365277740,88,11,'Yeah.','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 6th, 07:49 PM </br>I was in a hurry when i put &quot;rock collector ruby&quot; in.','Default',NULL,2,0),(115,1365439076,11,88,'Start Moves','Shuang on Apr 8th, 04:37 PM </br>So, how do you have the start moves set up? Like how Charizard learns Air Slash as a start move, but in the real games, you have to get a heart scale and bring it to the move relearner to learn the start moves... So how is it set up right now, since we neither have heart scales nor a move relearner. Or is it just not possible to learn those moves yet?','Default',NULL,2,0),(116,1365440434,11,88,'Pokemon Exclamations','Shuang on Apr 8th, 05:00 PM </br>Some of these messages are a bit strange. Although many make since, some don\'t. For example, my charmander says things like I don\'t feel well, and I\'m so MAD, yet he gains a happiness... This is really weird, unless he likes being mad or he likes not feeling well... Maybe you could base it off of there current happiness, so if it\'s higher, than they say things like I can\'t wait to battle, and if they have lower than base happiness, than they say things like being mad...','Default',NULL,2,0),(117,1365443167,88,11,'yeah','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 8th, 05:46 PM </br>yeah i will have to work on the phrases. I have been sick the past couple days so i haven\'t been on. I plan on changing the exclamation popup anyway to prevent the false evolving.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Start moves i don\'t know if they learn those. I don\'t think they will. I will update things when i feel better.','Default',NULL,2,0),(118,1365444360,11,88,'Hope you get better!','Shuang on Apr 8th, 06:06 PM </br>I hope you get better soon! I hated being sick, I couldn\'t do anything... And with the start moves, maybe we could just have the pokemon learn them right as they evolve, cause that\'d be really easy...','Default',NULL,2,0),(119,1365891722,11,88,'message','Shuang on Apr 13th, 10:22 PM </br>+1 Happiness<br />\r\nâ¢	Iâm ready for anything!<br />\r\nâ¢	Wow, Iâve seen so many cool things!<br />\r\nâ¢	Weâre the winners!<br />\r\nâ¢	We canât be beat!<br />\r\nâ¢	Letâs show what weâre made of!<br />\r\n+10 HP<br />\r\nâ¢	That apple tasted good!<br />\r\nâ¢	That was a good nap!<br />\r\nâ¢	Iâm feeling much better now.<br />\r\nâ¢	Hey! My cuts all better now!<br />\r\nâ¢	That water helped a lot!<br />\r\n+20 HP<br />\r\nâ¢	That was a great meal!<br />\r\nâ¢	Iâve slept enough, letâs battle!<br />\r\nâ¢	Iâm feeling great!<br />\r\nâ¢	My wounds are fine now!<br />\r\n-1 Happiness<br />\r\nâ¢	Why wonât we train more?!<br />\r\nâ¢	I miss homeâ¦<br />\r\nâ¢	I didnât do well enoughâ¦<br />\r\n-10 HP<br />\r\nâ¢	That apple tasted funnyâ¦<br />\r\nâ¢	Iâm not feeling too goodâ¦<br />\r\nâ¢	Iâm getting sleepyâ¦<br />\r\nâ¢	Iâm so thirstyâ¦<br />\r\n-20 HP<br />\r\nâ¢	Ouch! I stepped on a rock!<br />\r\nâ¢	Iâm tired.<br />\r\nâ¢	Can we please eat?<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(120,1365894249,11,88,'Types items','Shuang on Apr 13th, 11:04 PM </br>Normal â Soft Fur<br />\r\nFire â Burning Ember<br />\r\nWater â Misty Foam<br />\r\nElectric â Charged Batteries<br />\r\nGrass â Leafy Twig<br />\r\nIce â Frost Dew<br />\r\nFighting âSteroids<br />\r\nPoison â Poison Vial<br />\r\nGround â Fertilizer<br />\r\nFlying â Shiny Feather<br />\r\nPsychic â Heavy Book<br />\r\nBug â Shedded Bug Skin<br />\r\nRock â Rough Diamond<br />\r\nGhost â Holy Symbol<br />\r\nDragon â Ancient Scroll<br />\r\nDark â Firefly<br />\r\nSteel â Ball Bearings<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(121,1366075060,121,11,'took people out of battl','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 16th, 01:17 AM </br>Using my phone tell people to refresh','Default',NULL,2,0),(122,1366075140,121,11,'chat doesnt work with my phone.','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 16th, 01:19 AM </br>','Default',NULL,2,0),(123,1366769389,121,11,'I talked to kyledove','Rolyataylor2 on Apr 24th, 02:09 AM </br>Wasnt able to get your signed thing yet. BUT he did say he would give a shoutout for the contest! :D','Default',NULL,2,0),(124,1367693191,11,11,'Something','Rolyataylor2 on May 4th, 06:46 PM </br>Hello','Default',NULL,2,0),(125,1367693274,11,11,'NothingMushc','Rolyataylor2 on May 4th, 06:47 PM </br>wowoowwo','Default',NULL,2,0),(126,1367693428,11,11,'woooo','Rolyataylor2 on May 4th, 06:50 PM </br>woooo','Default',NULL,2,0),(127,1367696412,11,11,'hello','Rolyataylor2 on May 4th, 07:40 PM </br>wah','Default',NULL,2,0),(128,1367704411,56,11,'Hey lucky havent seen you in a little bit','Rolyataylor2 on May 4th, 09:53 PM </br>Hi how are you doing? Been a while. Anything new?','Default',NULL,2,0),(129,1367714989,88,11,'I got messaging working.','Rolyataylor2 on May 5th, 12:49 AM </br>Yeah I gotta still figure out how to navigate all these menus. i feel like it is confusing.','Default',NULL,2,0),(130,1367724588,11,11,'dkak;dck;a','Rolyataylor2 on May 5th, 03:29 AM </br>a;sjkd;k<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(131,1367736360,11,88,'','Shuang on May 5th, 06:46 AM </br>Awesome! It\'s kinda confusing, but it\'s better than it was before<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(132,1367736360,11,88,'','Shuang on May 5th, 06:46 AM </br>Awesome! It\'s kinda confusing, but it\'s better than it was before<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(133,1367736487,129,88,'Hi!','Shuang on May 5th, 06:48 AM </br>Hey, what\'s up? So yeah, now that the message system is working again, if you go online and see that there\'s nobody their, and you have something important to say, or you just wanna catch up or something, then feel free to use the messaging system :P<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee you around!','Default',NULL,2,0),(134,1367768811,88,11,'Do you like the Index Cards section?','Rolyataylor2 on May 5th, 03:46 PM </br>I added a progress bar to that section to help give a goal of sorts. I am thinking of adding the trainer log to the user profiles too. So you can show off who you defeated.','Default',NULL,2,0),(135,1367781963,11,88,'','Shuang on May 5th, 07:26 PM </br>What section? And I can no longer access my own page btw... Yeah, you should definitely add a trainer log.','Default',NULL,2,0),(136,1367795873,88,11,'','Rolyataylor2 on May 5th, 11:17 PM </br>Yeah still working on that.','Default',NULL,2,0),(137,1367806159,11,88,'','Shuang on May 6th, 02:09 AM </br>Oh, just saw the index card progression thing. Nice! I like it! It\'s gonna be useful<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(138,1368458414,11,11,'Nothing','Rolyataylor2 on May 13th, 03:20 PM </br>Yes','Default',NULL,2,0),(139,1368458591,11,11,'how','Rolyataylor2 on May 13th, 03:23 PM </br>ya','Default',NULL,2,0),(140,1368828302,11,88,'FB','Shuang on May 17th, 10:05 PM </br>I saw on our facebook page an ability to make ads. It costs some money, but do you maybe want to try it out?<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(141,1368993142,11,88,'Problems','Shuang on May 19th, 07:52 PM </br>Alright, so, first off, there is now no way of knowing which route I\'m on, none that I can see at least. Also, a player, Dalex16x is stuck behind a tree.','Default',NULL,2,0),(142,1368993190,11,88,'Strange lights','Shuang on May 19th, 07:53 PM </br>I noticed some strange light, and so I took a screenshot and sent it to you in your email','Default',NULL,2,0),(143,1368993529,11,88,'Teleporter','Shuang on May 19th, 07:58 PM </br>Not as important, but teleporters no longer work properly. One must click where they want to go, and then go to drawnimals.com','Default',NULL,2,0),(144,1368994878,88,11,'RE: Teleporter','Rolyataylor2 on May 19th, 08:21 PM </br>Yeah the items all do that for now. It will be an easy fix just gotta go through all the items tho.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAlso i fixed delex16x\'s position and put him in town02 hospital.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAlso facebook ads will be great when I get all the glitches fixed. might be a little while I gotta go out of town for a week so I won\'t be able to work on it this week.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI am thinking I will get working on the site in full steam again when school is nearing the end and i can cut my hours back at work. This is the busy season for my job.','Default',NULL,2,0),(145,1369181818,11,56,'reply','LuckyNana on May 22nd, 12:16 AM </br>No not really. I\'ve been on every now and then , just never caught anyone when I get on<br />\r\nMaybe we\'ll be on at the same time eventually.<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(146,1369427991,56,11,'lol','Rolyataylor2 on May 24th, 08:39 PM </br>yeah maybe as i work out more bugs more people will be online.','Default',NULL,2,0),(147,1369710490,88,11,'Ok','Rolyataylor2 on May 28th, 03:08 AM </br>Idea:<br />\r\nThis would speed up production of the site. But may take a little while to implement.<br />\r\nHere is the idea.<br />\r\nI will keep one city. that city will be permanent. it will be surrounded by an endless amount of trees. these trees can be cut using a pokemon\'s move 100 times depending on the pokemon\'s level. When it is cut it reveals tall grass underneath which has pokemon in it. When you cut a tree it is that way for everyone. Then you can use ember or something to burn the grass away.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe will keep the cities and the farm we have including the NPC\'s. And the cities will show up on the map. But to get to them you have to cut the trees to form a route to get to the city\'s.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis idea would eliminate the need to make map content except the cities.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI can make the trees grow back eventually, or something.','Default',NULL,2,0),(148,1369801308,88,11,'Updates kinda','Rolyataylor2 on May 29th, 04:21 AM </br>SO i am reworking the MMO server so chat doesnt work...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdded the ability to TAP left,right,up,down and face a direction though.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWill be done updating the server in a couple days along with the update.','Default',NULL,2,0),(149,1369876633,11,88,'','Shuang on May 30th, 01:17 AM </br>Alright, sounds like a plan. Finals for me will be over on Friday, so I shall get back to really actually working then<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(150,1369877054,11,88,'','Shuang on May 30th, 01:24 AM </br>I don\'t know how well this would actually work tho, we could implement for parts of the game, but I feel like if it was how that was for the whole game, it would be really boring. So, instead, for some routes, you could make it like that, maybe new routes, ones that haven\'t been implemented yet. And you could make it so that it\'s not just a bunch of trees, but more like, different sized trees, and then maybe streams to make natural boundaries/paths(depending on if drawnimal has a move like surf)','Default',NULL,2,0),(151,1369887018,88,11,'Yea','Rolyataylor2 on May 30th, 04:10 AM </br>I am thinking that we will keep what we have just gonna be testing the tree destroying system over the next couple weeks. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThen I will add back what we have when I get things stable again. The transition will make the map a continuous world as opposed to what we have now where there is a transition from place to place.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nthe game may look terrible for a few days... just a heads up.','Default',NULL,2,0),(152,1370722152,11,11,'non','Rolyataylor2 on Jun 8th, 08:09 PM </br>jjih','Default',NULL,2,0),(153,1370742103,11,11,'kllklkl','Rolyataylor2 on Jun 9th, 01:41 AM </br>hjljljkljkl','Default',NULL,2,0),(154,1370742372,88,11,'website layout sucks kinda bad','Rolyataylor2 on Jun 9th, 01:46 AM </br>but it will improve. sending you this so you can see the notify (!) next to backpack.','Default',NULL,2,0),(155,1371060688,11,88,'Ideas?','Shuang on Jun 12th, 06:11 PM </br>https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&amp;v=gmywDbnC5oc<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe new fairy type is interesting, adds a new way to battle, and I like how they did that way to interact with their pokemon, it would help players bond with the pokemon. You want to do something like that?<br />\r\n','Default',NULL,2,0),(156,1371161236,88,88,'Grass encounters','Shuang on Jun 13th, 10:07 PM </br>Make a sticky for yourself about cutting grass allowing for encountering pokemon','Default',NULL,2,0),(157,1371528706,11,88,'Beginning','Shuang on Jun 18th, 04:11 AM </br>So, the minimap is in the way of lots of the questions at the very begining of the game, and also, my friend is having troubles accessing the game from his laptop.','Default',NULL,2,0),(158,1371849730,11,11,'jljlkj','Rolyataylor2 on Jun 21st, 09:22 PM </br>j;kjljlk','Default',NULL,1,0),(159,1372911753,11,88,'Stuff to work on','Shuang on Jul 4th, 04:22 AM </br>Add popups that give you daily rewards, and gambling','Default',NULL,1,0),(160,1372911847,11,88,'Stuff to work on','Shuang on Jul 4th, 04:24 AM </br>Add popups that give you daily rewards, and gambling','Default',NULL,1,0),(161,1372911849,11,88,'Stuff to work on','Shuang on Jul 4th, 04:24 AM </br>Add popups that give you daily rewards, and gambling','Default',NULL,1,0);
